---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="text-primary mb-5 text-sm font-bold uppercase">Offers</div>
    <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold">Ways to work together</h2>
    <p>
        Start with a small audit, stabilize one workflow, or build an
        AI-assisted internal tool when the process is already business-critical.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div
            class="border-primary/40 bg-primary-soft/30 flex flex-2/5 flex-col justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border p-6 shadow"
        >
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold">
                    AI Workflow / Automation Audit
                </h3>
                <p class="text-primary font-bold">€500–€1,500</p>
                <p>
                    Find out where your current AI workflow, automation,
                    spreadsheet, or prototype is fragile.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold">Best for</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Messy prompt workflows
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Fragile n8n / Make / Zapier flows
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Spreadsheet-heavy processes
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold">Result</h4>
                <p>
                    Clear next step: keep it manual, stabilize it, or turn it
                    into software.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
            class="border-border flex flex-2/5 flex-col justify-between rounded-lg border p-6 shadow"
        >
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold">
                    Stabilization Sprint
                </h3>
                <p class="text-primary font-bold">€2,500–€7,500</p>
                <p>
                    Stabilize one repeated workflow that is becoming too
                    fragile, manual, or hard to run.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold">Best for</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Repeated business process
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Broken or unstable automation
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        AI workflow that needs structure
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold">Result</h4>
                <p>
                    One process becomes less fragile and less dependent on
                    copy-paste.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
            class="border-border flex flex-2/5 flex-col justify-between rounded-lg border p-6 shadow"
        >
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold">
                    AI-Assisted Internal Tool Build
                </h3>
                <p class="text-primary font-bold">€7,500–€20,000+</p>
                <p>
                    Build a focused internal tool around an AI-assisted or
                    operations workflow that is already business-critical.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold">Best for</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Repeated e-commerce workflows
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Internal operations tools
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Processes used by the team
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold">Result</h4>
                <p>
                    A reliable internal tool built around how your team actually
                    works.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-border flex-2/5 space-y-3 rounded-lg border p-6 shadow">
        <h4
            class="border-border text-muted w-full border-b pb-6 text-center font-bold"
        >
            Simple Website Without WordPress
        </h4>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-1/3 space-y-3">
                <p class="text-secondary font-bold">€1,500–€3,500</p>
                <p>
                    A clean, fast business website without WordPress, plugin
                    updates, or unnecessary backend complexity.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1/3 space-y-3">
                <h4 class="text-muted font-bold">Best for</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Small business websites
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Service pages
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:chevron-right"
                            class="text-secondary"
                        />
                        Landing pages
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1/3 space-y-3">
                <h4 class="text-muted font-bold">Result</h4>
                <p>
                    A simple static website that is easy to maintain and does
                    not depend on constant plugin updates.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
